Package: sagui
Title: Photometric Analysis Tools for Spectral Cubes
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Rafael", "S. de Souza", 
           email = "rd23aag@herts.ac.uk",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for photometry, segmentation, visualization, and
    robust summary statistics on hyperspectral and integral-field spectroscopic
    (IFU) data cubes. Includes utilities for region-based flux integration,
    background estimation, variance-aware summaries, and multiscale masking.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
